        {
            "text": "Prediabetes is highly prevalent in most populations globally, and worryingly, the majority of people with prediabetes are unaware of their diagnosis. 13 Thus, it is essential to screen all COVID-19 patients at the time of hospital admission with HbA1c and/or plasma glucose to identify those with prediabetes 14 so that they can be closely monitored and appropriate treatment can be initiated early to improve their prognosis.",
